$ON_XSTCNUM
Onevent CONTROL Call C_XSTCNUM(zc) From W1ITF10
Onevent AFTER_CHANGE Gosub AMM_XSTCNUM From W1ITF10
Onevent BEFORE_INPUT Call AS_XSTCNUM(zc) From W1ITF10
Return

Subprog AS_XSTCNUM(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
Local Integer INDIC : INDIC = indice
Raz mkstat
Call TEXTE(49730,GBOUT1) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(6028,GBOUTS) From OBJDIV
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_XSTCNUM(zc) From W1ITF10
Onkey   2 Titled GBOUTS Call S_XSTCNUM(zc) From W1ITF10
Gosub _AFF
End

Subprog C_XSTCNUM(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()
If !GWEBSERV
 ## Action CONTVCR
 Call CONTVCR(VALEUR) From TRTDIV
 If mkstat : GERR = 1 : GZONE = "XSTCNUM" : GZNUM = 49730 : Endif
Endif
If !mkstat
 ## Action STD
 Call C_XSTCNUM(VALEUR) From SUBITF
 If mkstat : GERR = 1 : GZONE = "XSTCNUM" : GZNUM = 49730 : Endif
Endif
Gosub _AFF
End

$AMM_XSTCNUM
Call AM_XSTCNUM(zc)
If !mkstat & GOBJET
 zoncou = "XSTCNUM" : Gosub APRES_MODIF From =GPROGRAMME
Endif
Return

